{"id": 2783, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些事会让你觉得“都2019年了，怎么还这样”？", "description": "那些看上去“落后时代”的事件都有啥？", "record_count": 8136, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190211175335Ut6xEH2hPl73qLRy.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-02-19T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 328192, "content": "催生娃", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582637}, {"id": 328448, "content": "1.对日本民众的歧视，仍称呼他们为\"小日本\"\n2.对某些国家(整个国家)深刻的偏见与蔑视\n3.对一些封建迷信的偏执", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1584748}, {"id": 328193, "content": "没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582637}, {"id": 328194, "content": "都2019年了，自制力还是很差", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588330}, {"id": 328195, "content": "别提2019了，自90年代后中国的艺术审美一直走下坡路。特别是影视", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1032011}, {"id": 328196, "content": "都2019年了，社会还是金钱之上", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846323}, {"id": 328197, "content": "都2019年了 还是学不会先爱自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588337}, {"id": 328198, "content": "看到题图，我以为是一个人加一个皇冠。都2019了怎么还有h帝?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954596}, {"id": 328199, "content": "发布朋友圈集赞免费送xx手机xx电脑xx黄金玉佩。都2019年了咋还有人信这个？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525257}, {"id": 337927, "content": "还是没变好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631103}, {"id": 345607, "content": "都2019年了，WDNM游戏还没分级，全国未成年？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063467}, {"id": 328200, "content": "属羊的女生命不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820731}, {"id": 328201, "content": "9102年了，我，还是我。\n一切都没有变化。\n很平庸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1587473}, {"id": 328202, "content": "都2019年了，乌合之众还是那么多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588351}, {"id": 328203, "content": "都9102年了怎么还觉得有男朋友的男生是怪物？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572483}, {"id": 328204, "content": "都9102年了，怎么还不能好好排队？", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908593}, {"id": 328460, "content": "都2019了，催婚还是这么多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1589237}, {"id": 328205, "content": "还对男性比女性宽容更多", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1435740}, {"id": 328717, "content": "都2019年了，怎么谈个恋爱都要旺夫脸，八字合", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384461}, {"id": 328973, "content": "2019年了、怎么还单着", "image": "img/option/option/20190222181922t0xDwgZ97IRSYovU.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1591282}, {"id": 328206, "content": "填写报销单时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582104}, {"id": 328207, "content": "都2019年了，大家还是只能在这里表达自己真实的想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1543990}, {"id": 328463, "content": "都2019年了，还认为家庭暴力是家务事？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527916}, {"id": 329744, "content": "都2019年了，还不能跟合不来的人离婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1595636}, {"id": 329745, "content": "都2019年了，咋还是没有对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1518215}, {"id": 328467, "content": "都2019年了，距离还是个问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1589259}, {"id": 334868, "content": "都9102了，还觉得人穷怪屋基？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298793}, {"id": 328213, "content": "都2019了，还天真的认为自己可以减肥成功( ‘-ωก̀ )", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "